  "display_fullname": "Villain Pets Dominator RadioactiveAssault Snipe Proton Volley Quick",
  "display_help": "Hurls a volley of alpha particles over an extremely long range. Proton Volley can bypass some of a target's defenses and reduce the target's Defense. This is a sniper attack, and is best fired from a distance as it can be interrupted. If you are engaged in battle this attack becomes instant-cast. If you are not engaged, it will do bonus damage. Affected enemies have a small chance to be affected by the Contaminated effect. Hitting Contaminated foes with single target Radioactive Assault powers cause a small burst of damage to foes near the target.<br><br><color #fcfc95>Damage: Extreme.</color><br><color #fcfc95>Recharge: Slow.</color>",
